BT 1 0 0 1 0 123 Tm 12 TL /F1 9 Tf 0 0 0 rg (The same energy loop that powers every cell in your body can power civilization. This is not metaphor -- it is the same) Tj T* (physics at different scale. Biology runs on a Bootstrap loop: sunlight -) Tj (> water charge separation -) Tj (> proton gradient -) Tj (> ATP) Tj T* (synthase -) Tj (> mechanical work -) Tj (> waste heat \(IR\) -) Tj (> recharges water -) Tj (> LOOP. The engineering version: sunlight -) Tj (>) Tj T* (photovoltaic/thermal -) Tj (> water splitting -) Tj (> hydrogen -) Tj (> fuel cell -) Tj (> electricity + water -) Tj (> LOOP. Both loops are closed. Both) Tj T* (run on water. Both are optimized at the same coherence boundary. Paper 28 proved water is the battery \(15,000 m? of) Tj T* -0.0591 Tw (membrane, 180 mV, 36 MV/m, 10?? rotary motors at 9,000 RPM\). Paper 29 proved the aluminum-water car works \(50 kg Al) Tj T* 0 Tw (+ 40 L water = 500 km, demonstrated at MIT and Purdue\). This paper closes the loop at civilization scale: solar-powered) Tj T* (aluminum recycling feeds cartridge distribution networks that feed vehicles and generators that return spent aluminum) Tj T* (hydroxide for recycling. Net input: sunlight. Net output: mechanical and electrical power. Net waste: zero. The Bootstrap) Tj T* (Engine is the mitochondrion scaled to a planet. The numbers are real. The chemistry exists. The integration has not been) Tj T* (done. This paper says: do it now.) Tj T* ET
